{"type": "article", "id": 27955, "title": "20 条假装合群的套路，违心又心酸 | 好奇心研究所", "description": "皮笑肉不笑，行动心不动。——@凡陳俗世庶明", "date": "2016-06-10T07:03:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 11405, "name": "好奇心研究所"}, {"id": 410, "name": "社交"}], "category": 3, "column": 33, "author": 101671, "comment_count": 64, "praise_count": 471, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703151514atJPZ9VNIwHEmvfg.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p class=\"\">好奇心研究所的微博（@好奇心研究所）和微信公众号（ID：QLab42）全面上线啦，关注就可以与所长亲密接触。<br></p>\n<p>1.  集体活动时，跟着发活动照片到朋友圈，互相点赞</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703151456UZSDczYhqCFln9PW.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>2.  夸朋友圈里的人类幼子很可爱很有天赋</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070315145709R68WqD3OXInobB.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">3.  搜集表情包，一言不合发表情</figure><div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\"></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703151457WYxJ5mQkUshb9q3F.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">4.  加了好多群，不说话</figure><div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\"></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703151458BtbSe0mOLWXJQRlz.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75416667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\"></figure></div>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>5.  我本来都不用微信的<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703151459oBuX1Ei7bCel6nDz.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">6.  看别人看的剧，玩别人玩的游戏</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703151500LPejQToHE1s8AcKM.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>7.  看热搜</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031515013JS0YUF5ls8OWdNG.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54545455\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>8.  看综艺</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703151502dJILcRUiu5hVPor1.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75416667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>9.  假装很污</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070315150390X7BFc2xGrN13ia.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>10.  去 KTV，并不想唱</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703151504crKZhCl483gsnAQ2.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65306122\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>11.  参加同学聚会</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031515052YCFkJ8K3Nis1ePv.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56153846\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>12.  聊不来就开启微笑模式</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703151506S79rElIpx3oOyadc.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>13.  模式升级，徐徐点头并发出“嗯”的声音</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703151506Hyk06FwTXI1Zmdla.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.87529412\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>14.  这个 idea 很赞（用力的大拇指</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703151508EARzeqGJDdwxclXt.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75225225\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>15.  吃火锅跟着一起去调点蘸料，但根本不沾</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703151509dyltCfpH5PGEijMh.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75217391\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>16.  我当然能吃辣了哈哈啊哈（涕泗横流</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703151510vI4PAuN73sVBfZTp.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>17.  我喝我喝</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703151511DM4pRWhVZ08qY6Pu.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.678\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>18.  对对对，我见过，我知道，我也是</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703151512PyJmSTUdaN1AGKwi.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.568\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>19.  我当然是直的！（惊讶脸</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703151513fqhuzPMBDxje7nkN.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>20.  哈哈哈哈哈泪哈哈哈</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703151514tnlLEm8c5D1YzT9f.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>动图来自：<a href=\"http://giphy.com/\">giphy</a></p>\n<p><i><a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/labs.html\">好奇心研究所</a></i><em>是好奇心日报的一个调查栏目，这是一个探讨各种生活方式问题的互动平台，它针对的可能是生活方式的变化和潮流，也可能是某个品牌的服务。你可以在这里投票、吐槽、表明态度。</em></p>\n\n\n"}